#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the user manual for &kphotoalbum; &mdash; a digital image "
"cataloguing software that supports annotation, browsing, searching and "
"viewing of digital images and videos. If you are not the type who likes "
"reading documentation, but rather just want to try out things, here are a "
"few alternatives:"
msgstr ""
"Ovo je uputstvo za &kphotoalbum; &mdash; digitalna slika softvera "
"katalogizacije koji podržava anotacije, pregledavanje, pretraživanje i "
"gledanje digitalnih slika i video zapisa. Ako niste tip koji voli čitanje "
"dokumentacije, već samo želite da isprobate stvari, evo nekoliko alternativa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Homepage</"
"ulink>, and look at the quick overview, screen shoots, and introduction "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"Idi na <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Početna </"
"ulink>, i pogledajte na brzi pregled, slike ekrana, i uvodne video-e."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &kphotoalbum;, and accept its offer for a demo (If this is your first "
"time you start it), or go to <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu and select "
"<guimenuitem>Run &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. That will load "
"&kphotoalbum; with a number of images, and let you browse around."
msgstr ""
"Pokreni &kphotoalbum;, i prihvatite ponudu za demo (Ako je ovo vaš prvi put "
"da ga pokrećete), ili idite na <guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu> i odaberite "
"<guimenuitem> Run &kphotoalbum; demo </guimenuitem>. To će učitati "
"&kphotoalbum; sa velikim brojem slika, i početi pretraživati okolo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer to print out this document, then you may find it as on long "
"PDF document at <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink>. A "
"direct link is available at <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index.php?"
"page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum;'s Homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da se ispiše ovaj dokument, onda ga možete pronaći i na velikom "
"PDF dokumentu na <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink>. "
"Direktna veza je dostupna na <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index.php?"
"page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum; 's Homepage</ulink>."

